### Test Gara API Endpoints

### Get all customers
GET https://localhost:7000/api/KhachHang
Accept: application/json

###

### Get customer by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/KhachHang/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create new customer
POST https://localhost:7000/api/KhachHang
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenKH": "Nguyễn Văn Test",
  "sdt": "0901234567",
  "diaChi": "Hà Nội",
  "email": "test@gmail.com"
}

###

### Get all cars
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Xe
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all services
GET https://localhost:7000/api/DichVu
Accept: application/json

###

### Get active services
GET https://localhost:7000/api/DichVu/Active
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all products
GET https://localhost:7000/api/SanPham
Accept: application/json

###

### Get in-stock products
GET https://localhost:7000/api/SanPham/InStock
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all invoices
GET https://localhost:7000/api/HoaDon
Accept: application/json

###

### Get statistics overview
GET https://localhost:7000/api/ThongKe/TongQuan
Accept: application/json

###

### Get monthly revenue
GET https://localhost:7000/api/ThongKe/DoanhThuTheoThang
Accept: application/json

###

### Get top services
GET https://localhost:7000/api/ThongKe/TopDichVu?top=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get top products
GET https://localhost:7000/api/ThongKe/TopSanPham?top=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get recent invoices
GET https://localhost:7000/api/ThongKe/HoaDonGanDay?soLuong=10
Accept: application/json

